OL,3,C12% increase in hate crimes and hate-
OL,4,Crelated incidents reported to gardai
OL,6,FThere has been a 12% increase in the
OL,7,Fnumber of hate crimes and hate-related
OL,8,Fincidents reported to gardai.
OL,10,FThe force said some 651 hate crimes
OL,11,Fand hate-related (non-crime) incidents
OL,12,Fwere recorded in 2023, up from 582 in
OL,13,F2022.
OL,15,FThese include 548 hate crimes and 103
OL,16,Fhate-related incidents, up from 510
OL,17,Fand 72 respectively in 2022.
