OL,4,Crelated incidents reported to gardai
OL,6,FThe most commonly recorded motive was
OL,7,Fanti-race (36%), followed by anti-
OL,8,Fnationality (18%) and anti-sexual
OL,9,Forientation (16%).
OL,11,FGardai said these three motives have
OL,12,Fbeen the most common in the past three
OL,13,Fyears, however, anti-nationality
OL,14,Fovertook anti-sexual orientation to
OL,15,Fbecome the second most prevalent
OL,16,Fmotive in 2023.
