OL,6,FMeanwhile the largest percentage of
OL,7,Fthese were recorded in public order
OL,8,F(27%), followed by minor assaults
OL,9,F(16%), criminal damage not by fire
OL,10,F(9%) and criminal damage by fire (3%).
OL,12,FThe largest proportion (44%) of hate-
OL,13,Frelated incidents occurred in the
OL,14,FDublin Metropolitan Region followed by
OL,15,Fthe north-western region (21%), then
OL,16,Fsouthern (19%) and eastern (16%).
