OL,6,FIn a statement, gardai said they
OL,7,Fcontinue to strengthen their network
OL,8,Fof diversity officers to support
OL,9,Fvictims and those affected by hate
OL,10,Fdiscrimination in communities around
OL,11,FIreland.
OL,13,FAt present there are more than 500
OL,14,FGarda diversity officers working
OL,15,Facross the country who engage with
OL,16,Fminority communities and individuals
OL,17,Fon a daily basis to provide them with
OL,18,Freassurance and address issues of
OL,19,Fconcern for them.
