OL,6,FChief Superintendent Padraic Jones
OL,7,Fsaid that while in one sense it is
OL,8,Fpositive that victims are coming
OL,9,Fforward to speak to gardai, it is
OL,10,Fdisappointing that incidents of this
OL,11,Fnature occur at all.
OL,13,F"Being targeted because of a
OL,14,Fcharacteristic has an enormous and
OL,15,Foften life-altering impact on a
OL,16,Fvictim, and as a society we must
OL,17,Fcontinue to reject hate and
OL,18,Fdiscrimination. Everyone has a right
OL,19,Fto live safely," he said.
