OL,6,F"I want to thank all those that
OL,7,Fsupport people of all ages and
OL,8,Fbackgrounds who could be vulnerable to
OL,9,Fthis crime, particularly those working
OL,10,Fin community-based groups, schools,
OL,11,Fclubs and the voluntary sector who
OL,12,Fconsistently demonstrate to people to
OL,13,Flive without prejudice toward one
OL,14,Fanother.
OL,16,F"I strongly encourage anyone that has
OL,17,Fexperienced or observed prejudice to
OL,18,Fplease come forward and report those
OL,19,Fincidents to us.
